          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "CYCLO"
                ],
                "institute": "2BLGLVN"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Two accelerators:",
                " 1. A 30-MeV proton cyclotron produces large quantities",
                "   (2 x 10.**12 /s) of N-13 nuclei by the 13C(p,n)13N",
                "    reaction",
                " 2. second cyclotron brings 13N+ ions to the desired",
                "    energy"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " Radioactive N-13( T(1/2) = 9.96 min ) beam"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SITA"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                " Three experiments have been performed:",
                " (i) the measurement of the partial gamma-width of the",
                "  N-13(p,gamma)O-14 resonance;",
                " (ii) the measurement of the resonance energy Er and",
                "      total width;",
                " (iii) the determination of the spectroscopic factor S",
                "  for the 13N(d,n)O-14 g.s. reaction to the O-16 ground",
                "  state (g.s.)."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "In these three experiments,",
                "  for (i) and (ii)) or deuterated (for (iii))",
                "  polyethylene targets  were used.",
                "  (CH2)n was 100-200 mu-g/cm2 thick.",
                "  (CD2)n was 50 and 300 mug/cm2 thick."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GELI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The gamma detection was carried out with two",
                "large volume Ge detectors, 70% and 90% efficiencies on",
                "the 1332 keV gamma-line of Co relative to a",
                "7.6 cm*7.6 cm NaI at a source to detector distance of",
                "25 cm."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SIBAR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A surface-barrier diode, positioned at 17.degr.",
                "with respect to the incident beam direction, detects",
                "the scattered 13N projectiles and the 13C and H recoils"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " two silicon detectors were mounted which recorded",
                "the scattered 13N and the recoiling deuterons."
              ]
            }
          ],
